models.name: ResNet50
models.description: Deep residual network for high-accuracy blood cell classification. Uses skip connections to enable training of very deep networks.

models.name: DenseNet121
models.description: Dense connections between layers enable better feature reuse and gradient propagation. Efficient and accurate model.

models.name: MobileNetV2
models.description: Lightweight model optimized for mobile and edge devices. Balances accuracy with computational efficiency.

models.name: ViT
models.description: Transformer-based architecture applying self-attention mechanisms to image patches. Novel approach to image classification.

models.name: YOLO v8
models.description: State-of-the-art object detection model for identifying and localizing blood cells in microscopic images.

models.name: Cell Counter v2
models.description: Specialized model for accurate counting of white and red blood cells. Uses density estimation and segmentation techniques.
